content: All stages are basically the same and there's no real penalty for hitting obstacles. The bad guy (Crusher) makes big machines to stop you, but these are just window dressing, get to the end of the level and Blaze automatically destroys them. You can transform into different machines yourself, but these are really just skins and don't affect gameplay.
For those who are stuck in the loading screen, just need to kill the app, add storage permission in the app info settings and then restart the game.
